		  2D4:  Call  SetTexPanner  ( ~Model:fgdarkness 4 )
		  2E8:  Thread
		  2F0:  	Set   *Var0  4
		  300:  	Set   *Var1  1438`
		  310:  	Set   *Var2  808`
		  320:  	Set   *Var3  710`
